extendedInfo.description: Big Lots Coupons -  Get 50% from your favorite brands. Register and generate coupons for your favorite brands and stores its easy to save with Big Lots Coupons. Enjoy this unique application and save money.

reviews.title: Zero stars
reviews.comment: Thought this app would be specifically for big lots, also downloaded the app for Lowes, they were the exact same app and it just takes you to a coupon website the shows random coupons, none of them were for any stores I\'d be interested in
reviews.author: mitch mckenzie
